.git
.gitignore
node_modules/
.next/
.venv/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd
.DS_Store
README.md
docs/
output/
# Exclude scripts/* (file-level glob so the parent dir stays visible
# and the negation below can re-include the api-test subtree, which is
# imported at runtime by src/lib/openapi-spec.ts -> /api/api-docs).
# Plain `scripts/` (dir-level) hides everything inside so the negation
# cannot work. See commits 1054ff1f3 and a2462fee2 — this is the third
# time this pattern has regressed via a sync-from-main merge. DO NOT
# replace these two lines with `scripts/`.
scripts/*
!scripts/api-test/
# Per-agent worktrees and tooling — never deploy
.claude/
keynote-mcp/
